dc_title_s: Pierhead and bulkhead lines for Hackensack River, N.J. in 3 sheets, sheet 2, from Paterson Plank Road Bridge at Secaucus to 3000 ft. below Overpeck Creek
dc_description_s: Map showing the pierhead and bulkhead lines of various business and private properties along the Hackensack River, from Paterson Plank Road Bridge at Secaucus to 3000 feet below Overpeck Creek. Also summarizes location of monuments with survey sketches.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|File No. 5/36 Hack. Riv.|Drawn by P.B.
